A( 3 , -1)
x^2+y^2+4x+8y+3=0
x^2+4x+y^2+8y+3=0\implies (x+2)^2+(y+4)^2=17
\;(a,b)\;
y+1=m(x-3)\iff y=mx-3m-1\;\;\text{(why?)}
